These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, lemonade, hot-chocolate
4 different pets are kept: snake, rabbit, goldfish, cat
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bus, taxi, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | coffee  | hot-chocolate | lemonade    | iced-tea       |
| Pet         | rabbit | cat    | goldfish      | snake |
| Transport   | roller   | taxi | bus | helicopter        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, spinach, lemon, garlic
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, entrepreneur, bartender, firefighter
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, subway, boat, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the firefighter##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the bartender is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the train is the photographer##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | lemon   | spinach | lettuce     | garlic      |
| Job         | entrepreneur | bartender | firefighter | photographer |
| Transport   | subway    | quad-bike   | boat     | train      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, chess, traveling, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, salsa, gospel, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, colombian, chinese, malaysian
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the fan of classical is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the fan of gospel##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
6. the malaysian is on the right of the chinese##1
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | cooking | chess | traveling | skydiving |
| Music-Genre   | classical       | salsa    | dubstep | gospel     |
| Nationality   | thai | chinese    | malaysian | colombian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, analyst, manager, nurse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, snowboarding, sailing, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, roller, scooter, helicopter
1. the manager is the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the analyst is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is tennis is the manager##1
7. the manager is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
8. the nurse is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | fisherman | nurse | manager | analyst |
| Sport       | snowboarding     | swimming      | tennis     | sailing      |
| Transport   | roller | bike         | helicopter      | scooter        |

