.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, filmmaking, fishing, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, superhero, drama, animation
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, weightlifting, soccer, golf
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the person watching drama movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person who's hobby is photography is the person watching superhero movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | fishing   | hiking | filmmaking  | photography      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | sports        | animation  | superhero       |
| Sport         | handball | soccer    | weightlifting | golf |

