.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, electrician, social-worker, firefighter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, thriller, drama, animation
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, blues, techno, jazz
1. the journalist is the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the firefighter##1
4. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
5. the electrician is on the far left##1
6. the person watching drama movies is the social-worker##1
7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
8. the firefighter is the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | electrician | social-worker | firefighter | journalist |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | drama  | thriller | spy   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | classical     | techno | blues       |

