.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-7::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, strawberry, cauliflower, kiwi
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, photography, drawing, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, comedy, adventure
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the far right##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person who's hobby is photography is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food          | pomegranate  | kiwi | cauliflower   | strawberry     |
| Hobby         | hiking | photography   | reading  | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy         | scientific  | time-travel | adventure  |

