.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, romance, documentary, action
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, colombian, indian, turkish
1. the person drinking mirinda is the indian##1
2. the turkish is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the indian##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the turkish is the person drinking fanta##1
7. the colombian is on the left of the turkish##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | fanta     | cola | mirinda |
| Movie-Genre   | action  | thriller | documentary       | romance    |
| Nationality   | colombian   | turkish | polish    | indian |

