.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapes, banana, zucchini, radish
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, soul, dubstep, electronic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, rowing, climbing, surfing
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating banana##1
5. the person eating banana is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | zucchini        | radish   | banana  | grapes   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae         | electronic     | soul    | dubstep       |
| Sport         | rowing | snowboarding | climbing | surfing |

