.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, tea, milk
There 4 different types of food: pepper, eggplant, papaya, carrot
4 different pets are kept: frog, rat, lizard, cat
1. the person drinking milk is the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | juice    | tea | milk | cola        |
| Food       | carrot | pepper  | eggplant | papaya     |
| Pet        | rat    | lizard   | cat  | frog |

