.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, journalist, paramedic, coach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, cycling, baseball, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, ship, motorbike, boat
1. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the journalist##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the coach##1
7. the person who's sport is swimming is the person driving the motorbike##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | architect  | coach | journalist  | paramedic |
| Sport       | baseball | cycling        | soccer | swimming       |
| Transport   | van   | ship          | boat          | motorbike       |

