The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, comedy, fantasy, martial-arts
There are 4 different nationalities: french, american, argentine, turkish
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the turkish is on the left of the french##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is the argentine##1
7. the turkish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | video-games   | sudoku   | hiking | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | spy | comedy   | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | turkish     | french  | argentine  | american  |

