.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, camping, gardening, photography
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, jazz, reggae, techno
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, basketball, biathlon, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the fan of techno##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the fan of techno##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | photography | camping    | writing        | gardening |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | reggae     | techno        | salsa   |
| Sport         | basketball   | snowboarding | biathlon | volleyball  |

