.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, martial-arts, spy, documentary
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, turkish, brazilian, italian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, van, snowmobile, trike
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the brazilian##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the italian##1
3. the nigerian is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the brazilian##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person driving the van##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
8. the turkish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | documentary  | horror    | spy    |
| Nationality   | italian | brazilian  | nigerian  | turkish |
| Transport     | trike  | van | snowmobile | bus        |

