.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, milk, juice
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, horror, musical, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, badminton, juice-polo, parkour
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person drinking juice##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is juice-polo##1
7. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching action movies##1
8. the person watching musical movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda        | juice    | almond-milk | milk      |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | martial-arts   | horror  | musical  |
| Sport         | parkour | badminton | juice-polo   | skateboarding |

