The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, zombie, action, time-travel
4 different pets are kept: goat, snake, hamster, ferret
1. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating onion##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the person eating blueberry is the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
6. the person watching action movies is the person eating grapes##1
7. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | onion     | cucumber   | grapes | blueberry |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | time-travel | action | zombie   |
| Pet           | ferret    | snake     | goat      | hamster     |

