.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-17::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, designer, journalist, engineer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, dubstep, salsa, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, japanese, dutch, polish
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the dutch##1
2. the designer is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the fan of rock is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the fan of salsa is the japanese##1
5. the journalist is on the far left##1
6. the engineer is on the right of the polish##1
7. the dutch is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | journalist  | dancer | designer  | engineer |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | rock       | dubstep | classical      |
| Nationality   | japanese | nigerian  | polish    | dutch    |

