4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the italian is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Nationality   | american | nigerian | italian | indian |
| Sport         | climbing | soccer | parkour  | skateboarding  |
| Transport     | helicopter  | bike | skateboard     | tram  |

