3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
4. the american is on the far right##1
5. the japanese is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the turkish is on the far left##1
7. the bartender is on the far right##1
8. the turkish is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Job           | photographer  | electrician  | accountant | bartender |
| Nationality   | turkish   | japanese | canadian   | american      |
| Sport         | cricket | volleyball    | weightlifting   | skiing         |

 